metadata.title: HuggleHounds Dog Toy for Aggressive Chewers - Extra Durable Interactive Toy for Dogs - Tug of War Chew Toy for All Breed - Non-Toxic Rubber - Tuffut-Lon Bobb - Wee | Made in USA
features: DURABLE DOG TOY FOR PUPS WHO LIKE TO CHEW: If you’re small pup or large canine loves to chew, then this dog tug of war toy bone will enhance his natural instincts.
CHEWY FLAVORED DOG BONE TOY: Your friendly Fido will not only love the ease of anchoring this dog tug of war toy, but also the grilled chicken flavoring that lasts the life of the dog chew toy.
DOG TOYS FOR FETCH AND CATCH: It doesn’t get more interactive then playing with a real-tuff Bobb dog toy that has a paw-friendly kickstand that is perfect for fetching and gentle tugging.
IDEAL PET TRAINING TOY: The durable nylon and style of this dog bone toy makes it the perfect option for pet training, especially for growing pups who love to chew and tug.
ENCOURAGE POSITIVE PET PLAY: This fun and rewarding dog chew toy is perfect for helping reduce pet anxiety while prompting interaction between dogs and their owners.
description: Our HuggleHounds Tuffut-Lon Bobb toy has what every (real-tuff) pup is after! Designed in our “bone-only-better” style and made of durable nylon, Bobb gives pups who love to chew the perfect toy to satisfy their natural instincts, along with the ability to anchor the toy with their paws. Yup, it’s like a built-in, paw-friendly kickstand! Bobb’s design also allows for easy tugging, toting and fetching. Can it get better? YES! Tuffut-Lon Bobb is flavored with our exclusive HuggleHounds Grilled Chicken flavoring that lasts the life of the toy! Yumm.
